CrowdTwist,is,a,customer,loyalty,platform,that,offers,companies,and,organizations,a,way,to,reward,their,customers,for,being,loyal,to,their,services,and,brands,With,CrowdTwist,companies,can,advertise,to,people,reward,people,for,being,customers,and,analyze,how,well,the,campaigns,are,working,The,CrowdTwist,API,allows,developers,to,access,information,from,CrowdTwist,Example,API,methods,include,retrieving,user,information,user,point,rewards,information,identify,locations,specific,to,users,and,view,user,activity